commit.message:
Customizable send_mail (#730)

* Make send_mail function customizable.
Docs for OAauth2-based custom login manager
Allow custom login_manager to be passed in to Flask-Security

docs: fix anchor links and typos

* Fix sphinx link issues in quickstart.rst.
  (closes #700)

Fix password recovery confirmation on deleted user

* Adds test case for password recovery on deleted user.
  (closes #678)

Remove automatic login on email confirmation

* Successful password reset redirects to login view by default.

* Successful email confirmation redirects to login view by default.

* Updated password reset tests to check user doesn't get 
  logged in automatically.  (closes #662)

* Added tests to test redirections on password reset 
  and email confirmation.
Make SECURITY_PASSWORD_SINGLE_HASH a list of scheme ignoring double hash
Add base template to security templates

utils: fix incorrect email sender type

* Fixes error when sending emails using Flask-Mail, without setting the
  SECURITY_EMAIL_SENDER (closes #685).
